{"tid":397554,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】PUBG戰友招募中 Day113 12/9","createTime":"2017-09-12T14:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T17:49:31.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03f3ca07d5d9155f8be219ea62c029af55f69888","tid":397554,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=hM2Fbn0eNX2kgcVWjfUFlf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e3f98ee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=hM2Fbn0eNX2kgcVWjfUFlf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5862e414\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=hM2Fbn0eNX2kgcVWjfUFlf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e5e54158\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"6bcefcebdeb8f8ba2fae6394cecfed9eb931fd7b","tid":397554,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb9e70af9be75f5c92c8be6a02f84cbf306443d","tid":397554,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cde07cb0342ae3caf571e6a189bb619f2ff1a8","tid":397554,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edfff5ebddaf18be6c0785e4f907013d3d107e4","tid":397554,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35aea8f04a05b0ea7f6981f01456c5efb47f701c","tid":397554,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71836b025735ccad53ecf397912ff5a52c75084","tid":397554,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7a0cc21f1245e0963205e2cbdc079c09522cbd","tid":397554,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7639d6c9cd7e08703db4861db53f81a0432dae","tid":397554,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" clas